-----MVP-----
- Signup/Login
- Upload Vidos
- View Videos
- Likes / Comments



=====FRONTEND=====
Html + Css + JavaScript + TailwindCss

=====BACKEND=====
Spring Boot REST API

=====Auth=====
JWT(Token-based)

=====Database=====
PostgreSQL

=====FileStorage=====
Firebase(MVP)

=====VideoHandling=====
FFmpeg (Transcode thumbnails + preview )

=====Hosting=====
LOCAL


------API STRUCTURE------
api/auth/ (Login/Signup)
api/videos/
api/upload/
/{id}
/
/{id}/like


------FrontEnd------
- Home (title + thumbnail + views)
- Upload (Form: title + description + file)
- Watch (Video Player + like + description)
- Login/Register (Username/Password)


======= MVP FEATURES =======
+ JWT (User Auth)
+ Form + Backend (Video Upload)
+ Firebase (File STorage)
+ Html5 Video (Stream Video)
+ One Per User (Like Button)
+ Auto-increment (View Count)
+ Pagination (Video List)
+ View without login (Public Access)


======= Advanced Features (Not in MVP) =======
+ Comments
+ Tags & Categories
+ Search by tile
+ Dashboard
+ AI transcription & search







